name: ENDLESS LIGHT The Blue Series Collection by Sketchlight

metadata.name: STREAMING (part 1)
metadata.description:
Limitless. 

Endless light is expressed by the fact that it spreads everywhere. It is a light that is not limited and revealed everywhere, even when it is not revealed in the world by its infinite being, it is everywhere openly.

Light Painting Photography (one single exposure)

Light painting is an art form, a technique that consists of creating Images by capturing the movement of light.
